sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant Vault as query_knowledge_vault
    participant Web as web_search
    Agent->>Vault: "what do I already know about X?"
    Vault-->>Agent: ranked hits (or nothing)
    alt vault has it
        Agent->>Agent: reason over local knowledge
    else gap
        Agent->>Web: search the web (then ingest)
    end
